Why does not understanding in mainland against Okinawa progress? One is that the amount and quality of Okinawa information on mainland media is causing a loss of public awareness. I realize that I read Okinawa paper everyday, but the Ryukyu Shimpo and the Okinawa Times reported detailed regional information daily.

According to Mr. Kazuhide Ueshiba @ okusa _ kazuhide, NHK reception fee payment is less than 50% in Okinawa nationwide. One reason is that there is a distrust of NHK, a public broadcaster and representative of mainland media, not reporting the reality too much against high-level coverage on the prefectural side including Okinawa media stationeries issue Okay.
